</div>

<%= h2_tag('Screens and Previews') %>
<p>Screens provide a visual aesthetic similar to a browser window for showcasing screenshots of projects.</p>
<p>Nesting a preview inside a screen provides a space to see a snippet of content and expand it when needed.</p>

<div class="screen">
  <div class="screen-title">Screen Component</div>
  <div class="preview" data-toggle="is-fullscreen">
    <div class="preview-content">
      <div class="panel">
        <p>Screens provide a visual aesthetic similar to a browser window.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
